<form action="/membership/clubMemberFormPreview" method="POST">
    <div class="card col-12" style="width: 740pt; background: transparent;">
        <% req.session.data = req.session.data || {} %>
        <br>
        <h1 style="font-size: 18pt; text-align: center;"><b>Preview 預覽</b></h1>
        <br>
        <h1 style="font-family: Verdana,Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;  font-size:16pt; color: #888888;">
            <b><u>Application for Club Membership 團體註冊申請</u></b></h1>
        <br>

        <ol type="A">

            <li style="color: #83a70c; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;">申請者資料 Particulars of Applicant</li>
            <div class="form-group">
                <span>機構 Organization :</span> <b><%= req.session.data.OrgEngName%></b> (英文 English)
                <br>
                <span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;:</span><b><%= req.session.data.OrgChiName%></b>
                (中文 Chinese)
                <br>
                <span>申請者姓名 Name of Applicant:</span> <b><%= req.session.data.AppEngName%></b> (英文
                English)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <b><%= req.session.data.AppChiName%></b> (中文 Chinese)
                <br>
                <span>地址 Address:</span> <b><%= req.session.data.clubAddr%></b>
                <br>
                <span>電話 Tel:</span> <b><%= req.session.data.clubTel%></b>
                <br>
                <span>傳真 Fax:</span> <b><%= req.session.data.clubFax%></b>
                <br>
                <span>電郵 E-mail:</span> <b><%= req.session.data.clubEmail%></b>
                <br>
                <span>網址 Web-site:</span> <b><%= req.session.data.clubWeb%></b>
                <br>
                <span>機構成員人數 No. of Members in the Organization:</span> <b><%= req.session.data.MemberNo%></b>
                <br>
            </div>
            <li style="color: #83a70c; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;"> 請簡單描述貴機構/團體/學校曾舉辦或參與的體操活動 <br> Brief
                description of gymnastic activities which the Organization /
                Club / School has organized / taken part</li>
            <b><%= req.session.data.brefDes%></b>
            <br><br>

            <li style="color: #83a70c; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;">體操活動的機構代表/負責人資料<br>Particulars of
                Organization Representative / Person in charge of the gymnastic
                activities</li>

            <div class="form-group">
                <span>姓名 Name:</span> <b><%= req.session.data.resEngName%></b> (英文
                English)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <b><%= req.session.data.resChiName%></b> (中文 Chinese)
                <br>
                <span>職位 Position held:</span> <b><%= req.session.data.position%></b>
                <br>
                <span>地址 Address:</span> <b><%= req.session.data.resAddr%></b>
                <br>
                <span>電話 Tel:</span> <b><%= req.session.data.resTel%></b>
                <br>
                <span>傳真 Fax:</span> <b><%= req.session.data.resFax%></b>
                <br>
                <span>電郵 E-mail:</span> <b><%= req.session.data.resEmail%></b>
                <br>
            </div>
            <li style="color: #83a70c; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;">致中國香港體操總會主席 To the Chairperson of GAHK</li>
            <span>The prescribed membership fee for the year of </span><b><%= req.session.data.year%></b><span> at HK$</span><b><%= req.session.data.clubFee%></b><span> and details of the Organization is attached.</span>
        </ol>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="form-group col-sm-10">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-info"
                    style="background-color: #83a70c; border-color: #83a70c;width: 150px; float:right"
                    onclick="message()">Submit
                    提交</button>

            </div>

            <div class="form-group col-sm-2">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger" style="width: 150px; float:right"
                    onclick="history.back()">Cancel
                    取消</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</form>

<script>
    function message() {
        alert("提交成功!! Successfully Submitted!");
    }

</script>